HEADWORD: Absque hoc
<hw>Abs"que hoc</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[L., without this.]</ety>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The technical words of denial used in traversing
what has been alleged, and is repeated.</def>⟦br⟧
